name: The Surfing Frenchie
description: Dale is a Surfing French Bulldog featured in Disney's live-action Lilo & Stitch. The $Dale token was launched by Greg Dutcher, Dale's owner, and Dale continues to produce content across social media as he surfs and skates around Hawaii. Dale is the only Disney-featured animal with a token, and his goal is to grow Bonk's holder base and audience through his socials and event participation. Dale's team's goal is to share Dale's joy with as many people as possible.
